## Verification Plan

### Automated
```bash
flutter analyze          # Zero warnings/errors
flutter build web        # Successful web build
```

### Manual
- Navigate through tabs, ensuring GoRouter URL changes appropriately dynamically highlighting sidebar tab variants.
- Open multiple modals securely triggering persistence to `shared_preferences`.
- Validate scaling limits utilizing Web Chrome Inspector tracking visual integrity down to typical Mobile sizes.
